include ./navbar

section.hero-wrap.hero-wrap-2(style="background-image: url('/images/bg_final2.png');" data-stellar-background-ratio='0.5')
  .overlay
  .container
    .row.no-gutters.slider-text.align-items-end.justify-content-center
      .col-md-9.ftco-animate.mb-5.text-center
        p.breadcrumbs.mb-0
          span.mr-2
            a(href='index.html')
              | Home 
              i.fa.fa-chevron-right
          span
            a(href='product.html')
              | Products 
              i.fa.fa-chevron-right
          span= `${product.title}`
            i.fa.fa-chevron-right
        h2.mb-0.bread= `${product.title}`
section.ftco-section
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-6.mb-5.ftco-animate
        a.image-popup.prod-img-bg(href='/images/prod-1.jpg')
          img.img-fluid(src=`/images/${product.imageURL}` alt='Colorlib Template')
      .col-lg-6.product-details.pl-md-5.ftco-animate
        h3= product.title
        .rating.d-flex
          p.text-left.mr-4
            a.mr-2(href='#') 5.0
            a(href='#')
              span.fa.fa-star
            a(href='#')
              span.fa.fa-star
            a(href='#')
              span.fa.fa-star
            a(href='#')
              span.fa.fa-star
            a(href='#')
              span.fa.fa-star
          p.text-left.mr-4
            a.mr-2(href='#' style='color: #000;')
              | 100 
              span(style='color: #bbb;') Rating
          p.text-left
            a.mr-2(href='#' style='color: #000;')
              | 500 
              span(style='color: #bbb;') Sold
              
        p.price
          if product.onSale
            span.price.price-sale= `$${product.price}`
            span.price= `$${product.salePrice}`
          else
            span.price= `$${product.price}`

        p
          | A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth.
        p
          | On her way she met a copy. The copy warned the Little Blind Text, that where it came from it would have been rewritten a thousand times and everything that was left from its origin would be the word &quot;and&quot; and the Little Blind Text should turn around and return to its own, safe country. But nothing the copy said could convince her and so it didn&rsquo;t take long until a few insidious Copy Writers ambushed her, made her drunk with Longe and Parole and dragged her into their agency, where they abused her for their.
        .row.mt-4
          .input-group.col-md-6.d-flex.mb-3
            span.input-group-btn.mr-2
              button.quantity-left-minus.btn(type='button' data-type='minus' data-field='')
                i.fa.fa-minus
            input#quantity.quantity.form-control.input-number(type='text' name='quantity' value='1' min='1' max='100')
            span.input-group-btn.ml-2
              button.quantity-right-plus.btn(type='button' data-type='plus' data-field='')
                i.fa.fa-plus
          .w-100
          .col-md-12
            p#numAvailable(style='color: #000;')= `${product.numAvailable} available`
        p
          a.btn.btn-primary.py-3.px-5.mr-2(onClick="addToCart(this)") Add to Cart
          a.btn.btn-primary.py-3.px-5() Buy now
   

include ./footer

